Get Manhattan Info

nybb = st_read("/data/nyc_parking/nybb/", quiet=TRUE)
manh = nybb %>% filter(BoroName == "Manhattan")
#plot(manh,axes=TRUE)
library(raster)
ext = st_bbox(manh) %>% .[c("xmin","xmax","ymin","ymax")] %>% extent()
r = raster(ext, ncol=800, nrow=2400)
r = rasterize(as(manh,"Spatial"),r)
